{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"setUserId:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"userId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username)."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events."}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"title":"setUserId:completion:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"}}}